# Tokenized Real World Assets (RWA) Platform on Solana

Build a production-grade dApp for fractional real estate ownership with compliance, real-time pricing, and a modern UI.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Technology Choices:**
> - **Anchor 0.32.x** with SPL Token (not Token-2022 for simplicityвЂ”Token-2022 can be a future upgrade)
> - **Pyth Network** for oracle price feeds (pull-based model)
> - **Next.js 14 (App Router)** + **Tailwind CSS** + **Framer Motion** for frontend
> - **Node.js + Express + MongoDB** for backend
> - **Phantom Wallet** via `@solana/wallet-adapter`

> [!WARNING]
> **Solana Toolchain Required:** You need Rust, Solana CLI, and Anchor CLI installed locally for smart contract development. The frontend/backend can run independently against devnet.

> [!CAUTION]
> **This is a large project (~50+ files).** I'll build it incrementally in phases. The smart contract layer is simulated for local dev since we can't compile Rust/Anchor in this environment, but all code will be production-correct and deployable.

