### Phase 2: Backend (Node.js + Express + MongoDB)

#### [NEW] [backend/](file:///c:/Users/Tushar/rwa-solana/backend/)

**Models:**
| Model | Fields |
|---|---|
| `Asset` | onChainId, name, location, description, images[], documents[], totalSupply, availableSupply, pricePerToken, propertyValue, annualYield, assetType, status |
| `User` | walletAddress, name, email, kycStatus, kycDocuments[], role (user/admin), createdAt |
| `Transaction` | txHash, userWallet, assetId, type (buy/sell/transfer/yield), amount, shares, priceAtTime, timestamp |
| `Portfolio` | walletAddress, holdings[{assetId, shares, avgBuyPrice}], totalValue |

**API Routes:**

| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/assets` | List all tokenized properties |
| `GET` | `/api/assets/:id` | Get asset details |
| `POST` | `/api/assets` | Admin: create new asset |
| `DELETE` | `/api/assets/:id` | Admin: remove asset |
| `POST` | `/api/buy` | Execute buy + record transaction |
| `POST` | `/api/sell` | Execute sell + record transaction |
| `GET` | `/api/portfolio/:wallet` | Get user portfolio |
| `POST` | `/api/kyc/verify` | Submit KYC verification |
| `GET` | `/api/kyc/status/:wallet` | Check KYC status |
| `GET` | `/api/transactions/:wallet` | User transaction history |
| `GET` | `/api/admin/stats` | Admin dashboard stats |

**Services:**
- `solanaService.js` вЂ” Interact with on-chain program via `@coral-xyz/anchor`
- `priceService.js` вЂ” Fetch Pyth price feeds via Hermes API
- `kycService.js` вЂ” Mock KYC verification system

