> 2. **Tailwind Version:** The request specifies Tailwind CSS. Should I use **Tailwind v3** (stable) or **Tailwind v4** (latest)? I'll default to v3 for maximum ecosystem compatibility.
> 3. **Mock vs Real Oracle:** Since we're targeting devnet, Pyth feeds may have limited asset coverage. I'll implement the oracle integration structure but use mock price data for properties that don't have real feeds. Is that acceptable?
